comment6.target=java.lang.String\ ajustarDirecaoPara(int,\ int)
comment6.text=\r\n\ Calcula\ qual\ dire\u00E7\u00E3o\ seguir\ (horizontal\ ou\ vertical)\r\n\ com\ base\ na\ posi\u00E7\u00E3o\ do\ alvo.\r\n
